text: Ceroplesis marmorata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Reiche in 1849. It is known from Ethiopia and Erythrea.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis marmorata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1849
